msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
msgid ""
"The target server must support HTTP/3 and the connection must use TLS.\n"
"Make sure the client's TLS configuration trusts the server's certificate:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
